comment: Covington (PHI) sets the screen on Brown (LAL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Brown (LAL) and Smith (PHI) make incidental contact on the perimeter.
L-Slash shows Clarkson (LAL) extends his arm but does not clear out Noel (PHI) as he is trapped on the sideline.
Hill (LAL) jumps vertically and legally contests Smith's (PHI) running floater.
Smith (PHI) makes body contact before he gets his hand on the ball and the contact affects Clarkson's (LAL) driving layup attempt.
Smith (PHI) throws an air punch after being called for the foul.
Hill (LAL) makes contact with Noel's (PHI) arm and the contact affects his layup attempt.
Clarkson (LAL) takes longer than 5 Seconds to inbound the ball.
Aldemir (PHI) makes contact with Clarkson's (LAL) body and the contact affects his layup attempt.
Johnson (LAL) makes body to body contact on the perimeter that does not affect Noel's (PHI) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Brown (LAL) cleanly strips the ball from Covington (PHI) on his drive to the basket.
Correctly called 24 Second Violation.
Clarkson (LAL) wraps up Sampson (PHI) and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Noel (PHI) shuffles his feet during his post move.
Johnson (LAL) cleanly blocks Robinson's (PHI) layup attempt.
Robinson (PHI) commits a take foul on Kelly (LAL).
Kelly (LAL) cleanly blocks Smith's (PHI) driving layup attempt.
Clarkson (LAL) jumps into Robinson (PHI) and initiates the contact as he gets caught in the air trying to make a cross court pass.
Kelly (LAL) pushes Noel's (PHI) hip with his left hand and the contact affects his layup attempt.
Kelly (LAL) makes incidental contact with Noel (PHI) after he releases the shot in the lane.
